Class InvalidMentionArgument

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.breadmoirai.breadbot.framework.parameter.internal.arguments.MentionArgument
      • com.github.breadmoirai.breadbot.framework.parameter.internal.arguments.InvalidMentionArgument
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CommandArgument
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    InvalidRoleArgument, InvalidTextChannelArgument, InvalidUserArgument

    public class InvalidMentionArgument
extends MentionArgument
    If this argument is a mention but not a valid mention. Only applies to User, Member, Role, and TextChannel mentions. The invalid id can be retrieved with getInvalidId();
